snippet: Annette Catino of QualCare Inc. says that business ties are built on the golf course, and that cooking a meal with other managers helps build a team.
abstract: Adam Bryant Corner Office column features interview with QualCare Inc president and chief executive officer Annette Catino discussing her management techniques.
